│ operation on `poison` results in `poison`.\n\nThus, the      │
│ transformation incorrectly changes a well-defined `true`     │
│ result into `poison` for the input `x = 0`, as correctly     │
│ identified by `alive2`.\n\n### 2. Analyzing `opt`'s          │
