│ the range's lower bound is greater than 0, the               │
│ transformation is unsafe.\n\n### 4. Proposed Edit            │
│ Point(s)\n\nThe fix is to add a check within                 │
│ `foldIsPowerOf2OrZero` to prevent this optimization when the │
