│ ### 1. Understanding the Issue                               │
│                                                              │
│ The core of the problem lies in an incorrect interaction     │
│ between an optimization pattern and LLVM's `range` metadata. │
│ The original code implements a check for "is power of two or │
│ zero": `(%x == 0) || (ctpop(%x) == 1)`. `instcombine`        │
│ attempts to simplify this to `ctpop(%x) < 2`.                │
